title: StarTalk Live! Exploring Our Funky Solar System
description: Join Neil deGrasse Tyson and astrobiologist Dr. FunkySpoon as we explore our surprising, funky Solar System, from Mercury to Pluto and what lies between. With Eugene Mirman, Sarah Silverman and Jim Gaffigan.
author: feed@startalkradio.net (Neil deGrasse Tyson)
